#
# API for gl/glu/glut in ATS
#

######

The TEST directory contains a list of GL examples:

GL-test1.dats: Hello, world! (a still square)
GL-test2.dats: A rotating square
GL-test3-1.dats: Stippled lines
GL-test3-2.dats: A circling dashed loop in the shape of a square
GL-test4.dats: A simple example involving texturing
GL-test5.dats: testing gluUnProject
GL-test6.dats: Starfield (originally by Nate Robbins)
GL-test7.dats: Randomly generated regular polygons
GL-test8.dats: A simple wall clock implementation

####### end of [README] ######
